# Termux Installation
```
install f-droid
install termux
install termux:tasker
remove f-droid
```

# initial command
```
pkg install git -y

GIT_REPO_URL='https://github.com/niranjanshr13/android-termux'
GIT_REPO_LOCAL_PATH="$HOME/android-termux"
git clone $GIT_REPO_URL $GIT_REPO_LOCAL_PATH
echo "source $HOME/android-termux/config/bashrc" > ~/.bashrc
```


